from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedShuffleSplit
stratfied_split = StratifiedShuffleSplit(n_splits=1, test_size=0.2, random_state=42)
for train_index, test_index in stratfied_split.split(df, df["income_cat"]):
    strat_train_set = df.loc[train_index]
    strat_test_set = df.loc[test_index]
